data.description:
Welcome to this amazing one-of-a-kind home in the heart of the historic Island-City of Plainwell, well known for 2 ice cream parlors within walking distance surrounding the Kalamazoo River and Sherwood Park. 
Pride of ownership radiates as this home has been remolded inside and out over the last six years, including: a beautiful new kitchen with bar, 3 new full baths, 200 amp electrical, plumbing, 95% efficiency furnace, drywall, river-rock siding and board n' batten shutters, engineered hardwood flooring installed throughout the main & upstairs, laundry moved to 2nd floor, conveniently right off the 4 bedrooms! Lifetime metal roof to keep you dry. So much new, can't mention it all!
Main floor features beautiful stained-glass doors, living room, kitchen, full bath, office space, formal dining room, and flex space with new barn door. Great sized 2nd floor primary suite has brand-new gorgeous private ensuite which features a walk-in tiled shower with corner seat, ½" clear glass bi-pass shower doors, double sink vanity, toilet, timeless white ceramic flooring, lighting, bead-board, chrome fixtures, and a pocket door. WOW! What a showstopper! 3 other good-sized bedrooms, and a full bath with laundry complete the upstairs.
Outside features a raised flower bed with seating to the new firepit, an 18ft. round ready-to-go above ground pool, and beautiful mature trees! Inside, a fully finished basement with a pool table ensures room for all. The attached enormous, lofted 2 bay garage offers endless storage (or finishing potential), and the beautiful brick and window-walled breezeway/3 season room with lit rafters and gas heater make getting from the garage inside such a treat! A cute front porch welcomes you and says, "I'm home!" Make this home yours today!
